        <mxCell id="notes" value="Implementation notes&#xa;&#xa;1. The retrieval path uses H_txt, H_img_sum, H_roi_flat, img_mask, and roi_mask.&#xa;2. H_patch is projected and flattened but currently not consumed after that.&#xa;3. LoRA is attached, then a later freeze over self.llm.parameters() also freezes LoRA params in current code.&#xa;4. Returned logits are flattened to [B * 6, 4] before leaving forward()." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999999;fontSize=12;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
